<L>__{exterior boat dock}
<A>__{the three are sitting on the aft deck of the tour boat. their feet are up on the railing. very casual, very relaxed. discussing the end of the world.}
<C>__{sloane}
<D>__{my step father's always going off about how when he was young he was committed to all these causes.}
